lib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1.Cfg\">TM1.Cfg</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> <span class=\"fn\">σ</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Cfg\">TM0.Cfg</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1to0.Λ'\">Λ'</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span>)</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Translate configurations from TM1 to TM0. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1to0.trCfg","kind":"def","line":523,"name":"Turing.TM1to0.trCfg","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.lean#L523-L525"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1to0.tr\"><span class=\"name\">Turing</span>.<span class=\"name\">TM1to0</span>.<span class=\"name\">tr</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">σ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_3}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">σ</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1.Stmt\">TM1.Stmt</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> <span class=\"fn\">σ</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Machine\">TM0.Machine</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1to0.Λ'\">Λ'</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The translated TM0 machine (given the TM1 machine input). ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1to0.tr","kind":"def","line":518,"name":"Turing.TM1to0.tr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.lean#L518-L521"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1to0.trAux\"><span class=\"name\">Turing</span>.<span class=\"name\">TM1to0</span>.<span class=\"name\">trAux</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">σ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_3}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1.Stmt\">TM1.Stmt</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> <span class=\"fn\">σ</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1.Stmt\">TM1.Stmt</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> <span class=\"fn\">σ</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">σ</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1to0.Λ'\">Λ'</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Stmt\">TM0.Stmt</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The core TM1 → TM0 translation function. Here `s` is the current value on the tape, and the\n`Stmt₁` is the TM1 statement to translate, with local state `v : σ`. We evaluate all regular\ninstructions recursively until we reach either a `move` or `write` command, or a `goto`; in the\nlatter case we emit a dummy `write s` step and transition to the new target location. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM1to0.trAux","kind":"def","line":506,"name":"Turing.TM1to0.trAux","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.lean#L506-L516"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/Pos