a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Cfg.q\">q</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\">S</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">c'</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Cfg.q\">q</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\">S</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.step_supports","kind":"theorem","line":188,"name":"Turing.TM0.step_supports","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.lean#L188-L192"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Supports\"><span class=\"name\">Turing</span>.<span class=\"name\">TM0</span>.<span class=\"name\">Supports</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Machine\">Machine</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">S</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The raw definition of a Turing machine does not require that\n`Γ` and `Λ` are finite, and in practice we will be interested\nin the infinite `Λ` case. We recover instead a notion of\n\"effectively finite\" Turing machines, which only make use of a\nfinite subset of their states. We say that a set `S ⊆ Λ`\nsupports a Turing machine `M` if `S` is closed under the\ntransition function and contains the initial state. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Supports","kind":"def","line":178,"name":"Turing.TM0.Supports","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.lean#L178-L186"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.eval\"><span class=\"name\">Turing</span>.<span class=\"name\">TM0</span>.<span class=\"name\">eval</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Machine\">Machine</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Part.html#Part\">Part</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/Tape.html#Turing.ListBlank\">ListBlank</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Evaluate a Turing machine on initial input to a final state,\nif it terminates. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.eval","kind":"def","line":173,"name":"Turing.TM0.eval","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.lean#L173-L176"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.init\"><span class=\"name\">Turing</span>.<span class=\"name\">TM0</span>.<span class=\"name\">init</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span></span>]</