\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Machine\">Machine</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Cfg\">Cfg</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Cfg\">Cfg</a> <span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> <span class=\"fn\">Λ</span></span> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The statement `Reaches M s₁ s₂` means that `s₂` is obtained\nstarting from `s₁` after a finite number of steps. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.Reaches","kind":"def","line":166,"name":"Turing.TM0.Reaches","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.lean#L166-L168"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/PostTuringMachine.html#Turing.TM0.step\"><span class=\"name\">Turing</span>.<span class=\"name\">TM0</span>.<span class=\"name\">step</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Γ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Λ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"